qa.soul_desc: Meowster has prepared soul identification questions for you. Based on your answers, it will find a cat that matches you.
qa.q1:
At a party,
you’re more likely to
qa.q1_a1: Chat enthusiastically with lots of people and feel energized
qa.q1_a2: Find a quiet corner to talk with close friends and soon feel like heading home
qa.q2: When starting a new project, you tend to:
qa.q2_a1: Rely on past experiences and proceed step by step
qa.q2_a2: Envision the big picture and possible future directions before diving into details
qa.q3: When a friend shares their troubles, you usually
qa.q3_a1: Help analyze the root of the problem and suggest solutions
qa.q3_a2: Offer comfort first and express empathy and support
qa.q4: When planning a trip, you prefer to
qa.q4_a1: Arrange the itinerary, hotels, and routes in advance to stay organized
qa.q4_a2: Just book a flight and go, enjoying the freedom to explore spontaneously
qa.cat_desc2: Carries their own quiet aura, never needy — yet once they choose you, they’ll be your loyal companion for life.
qa.cat_desc3: Warm and caring, always offering gentle companionship that gradually brings peace to your heart.
qa.cat_desc4: With a lively spirit and a love for exploration, they roam freely, eyes shining with dreams of the world.
